@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_dnvjao(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((wp.cos(tmp + 0.31) / v0) + (wp.exp(tmp + 0.67) * wp.exp(v1 + 0.48)))
    v2 = 0.94
    tmp = (tmp + ((v0 + 0.51 - v2 + 0.08) * wp.abs(v1 + 0.33)))
    v0 = ((wp.sin(v0 + 0.15) - 0.26) - ((v1 + 0.88 * v1 + 0.97) * v0))
    data[tid] = v0
